%section#sponsoring_plans.paper
  %h2
    Travis CI crowd funding company packages
  %p
    There will be 3 regular types of packages: Platinum, Gold and Silver.  The basic idea behind these is:

  %ul
    %li
      %strong Platinum
      we will do everything we can in order to drive attention to these sponsors. They get the biggest amounts of space, will be displayed most often and get special attention from us personally.
    %li
      %strong Gold
      basically the same as Platinum but with about 50% amount of the space and they will be usually displayed with a second Gold sponsor next to them.
    %li
      %strong Silver
      we will also try to drive as much attention to them as possible but these spots are not limited and thus space will be even more limited and banners will appear in slightly bigger lists and in fewer places.

  %p
    Platinum spots will be limited to 4, Gold spots to 8, while Silver spots will not be limited technically.
  %p
    We might also sell "Special" packages for the same amount as Platinum packages.  These packages will only be available for deals that do not use or significantly conflict with the banner spaces used by any of the regular packages. For example Stripe.com is interested in placing a small banner at the top of the order form and bottom of order confirmation emails expressing that we use Stripe for payments.
  %p
    Next to these crowd funding packages we will summarize existing sponsors that pay for workers as "Worker sponsors". The sponsor of the worker box that has run a build will be mentioned and linked to in every build log.
  %p
    All sponsoring packages will last as long as the Travis CI crowd funding campaign lasts, but at least X months (to be defined).
  %p
    We are going to provide space for banners, texts and links in the following places:

